claim.claim-text:
A method for applying a glass protective pressure-sensitive adhesive sheet to an outer surface of an automobile glass window, the method comprising

a step of obtaining an edge sheet piece and a center sheet piece as the glass protective pressure-sensitive adhesive sheet;

a step of applying the edge sheet piece to a periphery of the automobile glass window; and

a step of applying the center sheet piece over the edge sheet piece;

wherein, in the step of applying the center sheet piece, outer margins of the center sheet piece are laid over inner margins of the edge sheet piece.
